  "title": "Flavorful Saudi Arabian Yellow Split Peas Pilaf",
  "description": "A traditional Saudi Arabian dish featuring yellow split peas in a creamy and yeasty pilaf, perfect for a solo dinner, this recipe combines the flavors of a mirepoix base with Mediterranean friendly ingredients.",
