  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion, carrot, and celery and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the yellow split peas, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the dissolved yeast and chicken broth, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and let it rest for 5 minutes.",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and serve hot."
